{"tid":146010,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"邪道紅白機mini襲港　內藏930款遊戲仲要玩埋PC Engine","createTime":"2017-03-06T16:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T04:05:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc7888907455e1984bbf4735e89f1bb514cf13b","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170303/org/1488468617_51b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170303%2Forg%2F1488468617_51b9.jpg&h=3d055dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/02/3289752/20170303_Vsub259AD_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F03%2F02%2F3289752%2F20170303_Vsub259AD_clean_w.mp4&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2939f25d\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/02/3289752/20170303_Vsub259AD_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new1.jpg&h=5f483a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 最近網上出現了「邪道版」紅白機mini，據稱機身內置有930款遊戲。 <br />\n <br />\n任天堂紅白機mini在香港一直熱賣，除了一眾老Gamer買來懷舊一番外，經典的遊戲內容、與小巧可愛的機身設計，亦令人愛不惜手；紅白機mini暫時在香港只引進了水貨版，一般市面炒價為$600-$700不等，不過記者最近在網上發現以更高價開賣的「邪道版」紅白機mini！與大家平時所見的正版紅白機mini不同之處，是原裝版只內置有經典的30款遊戲，但「邪道版」紅白機mini，竟然內置有930款遊戲，而且價錢更以近$1,300的高價作兜售。 <br />\n <br />\n記者在網上購得一部，基本機身外形及設計，完全是正版的紅白機mini，不過在開機打開主介面時，會發現除跟機的30款遊戲，還另加了兩個大型檔案夾，一個為「more games」，進入其內會發現有由A至Z排序的子檔案夾，再進入其內會發現更多的任天堂遊戲，據數碼潮流達人阿志表示：「這些子檔案夾，大概內藏有800餘款遊戲，它們分別是紅白機盒帶遊戲及磁碟機遊戲，相信絕對未能取得任天堂的授權，可能會涉及版權的問題。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new2.jpg&h=d1c73dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 我們找來了一直有賣水貨紅白機mini的數碼潮流達人阿志，為我們作出測試。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new3.jpg&h=1d6d3d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 開機進入主介面，發現多出了more games的檔案夾。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new4.jpg&h=17a83445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 進入more games會發現內裏有二十多個子檔案夾，內裏收藏了大量懷疑未經掤權的紅白機盒帶遊戲及磁碟機遊戲。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n在主介面的的另一個新增的檔案夾，則被命名為「PCE」，當打開一看時，則發現內裏加入了十數款的PC Engine經典遊戲，阿志續說：「想當年，任天堂與PC Engine分別是兩部不同廠商的遊戲主機，而且更是打對台的！所以在紅白機mini內出現它們的遊戲，更可以清楚表明這部機可能經過黑客的程式改寫手段，硬將非法遊戲加入其內；大家須知在香港，如果進行『非法改機』，香港海關已可作出拘控。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new5.jpg&h=db0234db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 這些遊戲，絕非原非授權的30款遊戲。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new6.jpg&h=558d3338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 由主介面進入另一個命名為PCE的檔案夾，會發現十餘款PC Engine的懷疑未經授權遊戲。 <br />\n <br />\n就今次發現非法改機問題，記者曾查詢香港任天堂，據負責人表示，暫時未能作出詳細回應或採取任何行動，但會就事件會向日本總公司匯報，然後再考慮進一步行動。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new7.jpg&h=992733a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 據阿志稱，這個改機手段，最早由俄羅斯黑客想出來。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170303/large/03sub259new8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F03sub259new8.jpg&h=4007210a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 記者曾到深水埗腦場放蛇找人改機，所有店員都耍手兼擰頭，異口同聲說非法改機，隨時會被海關拉人兼封艇。"},{"pid":"2511dc4250e24e094f2f1c9c7b8bac322bc923d0","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaef378238cf934d850fa0dc0efda19fb7b310c6","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5df95d3d81af7255898b6f52f6b3d5df2eba29","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41aedfeb5ce9de443a770fecc011f8e2bb3b6987","tid":146010,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:55:05.000Z","msg":"成千蚊玩呢d 小遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其買隻no man's sky J 畫面仲好"},{"pid":"0d6de9c8ab298a32aa33adb1a76a2e2283410117","tid":146010,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"有d興趣"},{"pid":"e7539f0be0350ea71a2d352e0711f211938593d1","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7786832ead5e0f17d745c2f7e2fba07e810eaf9d","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e7174bef99904f6848041b57240a64246b0d06","tid":146010,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}